data.description: Back on the market at no fault of the home or sellers.  Well maintained home features an open floor plan with large great room, updated hardwood flooring with carpets in the bedrooms, and vaulted ceilings.  Kitchen includes refrigerator, microwave, gas range and breakfast nook.  Sizeable main bedroom with dual sinks, walk-in closet, and tub/shower.  Cozy covered patio with turf grass and rock landscaping in front yard.  Location is minutes to shopping and restaurants.  Perfectly priced maintained home.
